(: XQuery nested inside HTML :)
(: declare namespace tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"; :)
<html>
<head>
<title>IGLouvre - Biblio - Contrôle qualité</title>
<style type="text/css"> 
<!-- 
